00:02:14.400 --> 00:02:23.120
headmaster of a school, surgeon and my dad doing what he did. The girls became school teachers

00:02:23.120 --> 00:02:30.000
and headmistresses of various schools, which was quite rare really in the 50s and early 60s.

00:02:31.840 --> 00:02:39.040
After finishing school at the age of 18, my dad decided to work for a while because he had to

00:02:39.040 --> 00:02:45.360
raise money to come to Britain and to take a degree. He'd applied to study medicine in

00:02:45.360 --> 00:02:52.800
St Andrews in Edinburgh and his plan was that it would take him about 10 years to raise sufficient

00:02:52.800 --> 00:03:00.240
funds to fund his course and fund his time in Britain. In the meantime of course he met my

00:03:00.240 --> 00:03:08.000
mother and life takes on a different course. They got married. My mum came from quite a very

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:16.640
quite a wealthy background and it was a match made in heaven actually because

00:03:18.560 --> 00:03:23.040
they would both be sotted with each other from the moment they met. It was a love marriage,

00:03:23.040 --> 00:03:33.040
not arranged, you know, contrary to the normal Asian expectation of life. And they were happily

00:03:33.040 --> 00:03:43.440
